/span></p></td></tr><tr class="c18"><td class="c15" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c30"><span class="c8">CERTIFICATION AND UNDERTAKING</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c12"><td class="c40" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c6 c27"><span class="c16"></span></p><p class="c39"><span class="c14">I UNDERTAKE TO ABIDE BY THE RULES AND REGULATIONS OF THE AGENCY, INCLUDING ITS CODE OF DISCIPLINE, OR THAT WHICH MAY HEREAFTER BE ADOPTED AND PROMULGATED AND TO SUBMIT MYSELF TO THE REQUIREMENT</span></p><p class="c28"><span class="c14">OF THE AGENCY WHICH ARE NOW AND MAY HEREAFTER BE DEMANDED, AMONG WHICH ARE :</span></p><ol class="c36 lst-kix_list_1-0 start" start="1"><li class="c34 li-bullet-0"><span class="c13">To have a valid and legal license while on duty.</span></li><li class="c33 li-bullet-0"><span class="c13">To submit authenticated certification of security license from SOSIA.</span></li><li class="c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c13">To submit updated physical / medical examination (New Applicants).</span></li><li class="c33 li-bullet-0"><span class="c13">To undergo physical/medical examination and submit updated Neuro-Psychiatric examination to be renewed annually.</span></li><li class="c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c13">To submit updated Drug Test Examination and to be renewed annually.</span></li><li class="c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c13">To submit updated NPC &amp; Barangay Clearance and to be renewed together with LESP.</span></li><li class="c33 li-bullet-0"><span class="c13">To submit updated RLM and to be renewed before its expiry date.</span></li><li class="c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c13">To inform the head office in writing and submit pertinent documents in case of change in address and civil status.</span></li></ol><p class="c20"><span class="c16"></span></p><p class="c6"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 4.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 688.80px; height: 146.40px;"><img alt="" src="images/image1.png" style="width: 688.80px; height: 146.40px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c20 c38"><span class="c16"></span></p><p class="c20 c38"><span class="c16"></span></p><p class="c17"><span class="c5"></span></p><p class="c17"><span class="c5"></span></p><p class="c17"><span class="c5"></span></p><p class="c21"><span class="c5">CONFORME</span><span class="c35">:</span></p><p class="c3"><span class="c4">I,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;, hereby acknowledge and confirm that I have read</span></p><p class="c10 c22"><span class="c4">and understood the&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Security and Investigative Services, Inc. Privacy Notice. By signing below, I give my explicit consent to the collection and processing of my personal data in accordance with the terms outlined in the Privacy Notice.</span></p><p class="c10"><span class="c4">Additionally, I authorize the company to inquire from my present and previous employers or references any and all information which may be sought by them, including details regarding my work habits, character, or skills. I further submit to the authority and discretion of the agency to assign and transfer me to any detachment as needed.</span></p><p class="c20"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c20"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c11"><span class="c29"></span></p><p class="c26"><span class="c42">Signature over printed name Date Signed :</span></p></td></tr></table><p class="c20"><span class="c16"></span></p><p class="c11"><span class="c37"></span></p><p class="c7"><span class="c13">3 of 3&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;REC-PDF-FOR02/2024</span><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.